Description: The `mxfda` package contains tools for analyzing spatial single cell data
  using methods from functional data analysis. While examples in vignettes illustrate 
  the use of the package for single-cell multiplex imaging data, the package can handle
  analysis of other types of point process data as well, 
  including repeated samples of spatial transcriptomics and geospatial data.
  Analyses for this package are executed and stored using an S4 object of class `mxFDA`. 
